      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "STREAM IT (6) wasn't far away at the finish when 5th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (25.03) at this track. The form out of his last race has been franked. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. OUR BANK (7) was speedy out of box 2 on debut to score by half a length (22.89) at Warragul over 400m. Drawn wide but has good early pace. Harder here but will be in this for a long way. MANILA JACK (1) ran below best last time finishing fourth (23.14) over 400m at Warragul from Box 2. Great chance to atone. ASTON NEWSON (4) took charge early and was never headed last time out. Big chance again.",
